&lt;h3 id=&#34;42-combinational-logic-组合逻辑&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#42-combinational-logic-组合逻辑&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 4.2 Combinational Logic 组合逻辑&lt;/h3&gt;
